snippet.title: Survive Into Night - Face the Undead Trailer
snippet.description:
Wishlist Survive Into Night on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1581380/Survive_Into_Night/

Face the Undead trailer for Survive Into Night - Coming Summer 2021! Survive Into Night is an upcoming indie game - A 2d top down action Survival Horror game. This isn't a nightmare it's a daymare!

Background music by TeknoAXE's Royalty Free Music | Synthwave C

Thank you to my Patrons at https://www.patreon.com/RealNotFamous for supporting this channel and providing the financial security to keep it running and build into a powerful business to help others!
